---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Sports Cardiac Assessment — Dr Delhasse, Cardiologist" description="Sports cardiology assessment: stress test, cardiovascular evaluation for amateur and competitive athletes in Valais." lang="en">

  <section class="hero-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Sports <span class="text-primary">Assessment</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Practise your passion safely</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container detail-content">
      <img src="/images/svg/expertise/Evaluation-a-la-pratique-sportive.svg" alt="Sports assessment" class="detail-icon" />

      <p>A sports assessment with a cardiologist is important for practising physical activity safely. A stress test is performed based on individual characteristics and the intensity of physical activity.</p>

      <h2>When is a sports evaluation recommended?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>When resuming sport after a prolonged break</li>
        <li>For competitors or practitioners of intense disciplines such as marathons or diving</li>
        <li>In case of a family history of cardiovascular disease</li>
        <li>With symptoms (chest pain, palpitations)</li>
        <li>With cardiac conditions such as hypertension or after a heart attack</li>
        <li>After cardiac events (surgery, stent)</li>
        <li>For seniors and at-risk individuals (diabetes, obesity) wishing to stay active</li>
      </ul>

      <p>It helps prevent complications and maximise the benefits of sport on the heart, in a region like Valais where sport is an integral part of the lifestyle.</p>

      <div class="detail-cta">
        <a href="/en/areas-of-expertise" class="btn btn--outline">&larr; All areas</a>
        <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Book an appointment</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-page { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-navy) 0%, #1a3d6d 100%); padding: 6rem 0 4rem; color: var(--color-white); }
  .hero-page h1 { color: var(--color-white); font-size: 2.75rem; }
  .hero-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 1.15rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .detail-content { max-width: 800px; }
  .detail-icon { width: 80px; height: 80px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .detail-content p { font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-gray); }
  .detail-content h2 { margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .detail-content ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .detail-content li { list-style: disc; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--color-gray); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; }
  .detail-cta { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .hero-page h1 { font-size: 2rem; } }
</style>
